message.text:
92-year-old Japanese Woman, Hisako Sakai, known for playing Claudio, goes viral after winning a Tekken 8 tournament designed to help active, healthy lives for seniors.

She also becoming one of the oldest esports winner ever. 

Source: Automaton Media
